\par }\pard\plain \fi567\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \lang2057\cgrid {\lang1033\cgrid0 When he got back to his room he was touched to find a
ll his belongings put away and in the bathroom his toothbrush and shaving things neatly arranged at one end of the glass shelf over the wash\_basin. At the other end was Vesper's toothbrush and one or two small bottles and a jar of face\_cream.
